<div class="row">
  <div class="large-12 medium-12 columns main">
     <h1><%= image_tag('new_logo.png', alt: 'Logo', 'data-interchange' => "[#{image_path('new_logo.png')}, (retina)]") %></h1>
     <p>
      Tucked away on its own bend along the stream, perched under a grove of black oaks,
      the Yosemite Bug Rustic Mountain Resort has a magical feel. Located only
      26 miles away from Yosemite Valley along California's scenic,
      open all year Highway 140. The Bug offers a relaxed and social
      atmosphere where families, backpackers and international travelers
      all find welcome and a variety of affordable accomodations and amenities
      an old time mountain resort would have.
     </p>
     <p>
      <b>"One of our favorite places to stay..."</b>
       <a href="http://www.latimes.com/travel/la-tr-d-escape-yosemite-20150705-story.html">LA Times July 4, 2015</a>
     </p>
  </div>
      <div class="large-12 columns">
     <%= image_tag('social.png', alt: 'Logo', 'data-interchange' => "[#{image_path('social.png')}, (retina)]") %>
    </div>
</div>
<hr />

<div class="row">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="large-6 medium-6 columns homebody">
      <h1>Value</h1>
      <p>At the Bug we feature a variety of lodgings to suit any budget.
        From well appointed private rooms in cabins, vacation rentals,
        to tent cabins and Hostelling International licensed hostel dorms.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="large-6 medium-6 columns homebody clear-fix">
      <%= image_tag('rooms/MonoLakeBxLodgingImageCarousel.jpg', alt: 'Logo', 'data-interchange' => "[#{image_path('rooms/MonoLakeBxLodgingImageCarousel.jpg')}, (retina)]") %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="large-6 medium-6 columns homebody">
      <h1>Quality</h1>
      <p>At the Bug we continue to focus upon the freshest fare with quatily ingredients
        We do our best to source locally, including our own garden.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="large-6 medium-6 columns homebody clear-fix">
      <%= image_tag('garden.png', alt: 'Logo', 'data-interchange' => "[#{image_path('garden.png')}, (retina)]") %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="large-6 medium-6 columns homebody">
      <h1>Rejuvinate</h1>
      <p>The Yosemite Health Spa provides a beautiful and relaxing atmosphere for
        travelers to restore their bodies after their adventures in the area</p>
    </div>

    <div class="large-6 medium-6 columns homebody clear-fix">
      <%= image_tag('garden.png', alt: 'Logo', 'data-interchange' => "[#{image_path('garden.png')}, (retina)]") %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="large-6 medium-6 columns">
    <h4>Latest News:</h4>
    <div class="panel">
      <h5> <%= @article.title %> </h5>
      <h6 class="subheader"> <%= truncate( @article.content, length: 800, separator: " ", :escape => false) %> </h6>
      <a href="#" class="small button">Read More</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="large-6 medium-6 columns">
    <h4>Recent Tweets:</h4>
     <p><%= render :template => 'tweet_feed/index' %></p>
  </div>
</div>

